airText: Economy Flex lets you choose your seats for free, and you can enjoy more baggage allowance and more flexibility to change your booking.

Economy Flex includes:

 Free seat selection and paid seat selection
 Earn 0.7 Skywards Mile for every mile flown
 Checked baggage allowance
 Cabin baggage 1 bag up to 7kg
 Regional multicourse dining
 Complimentary alcoholic and non-alcoholic drinks
 Up to 5,000 channels of entertainment
 Free unlimited online chat messaging for Emirates Skywards Gold members 
 Buy great value Wi-Fi plans
 Changes permitted for a fee 
 Refunds permitted for a fee

Please refer to the terms and conditions of the fare and the rules of the destination
 Please note that if the flight is operated by another airline then the onboard product or service will vary. The content on this screen is for information purposes only. Please validate brands and ancillaries at Fare Quote.
Includes rebooking or refunds against a fee, and seat reservation
ECONOMY SMART - our recommended fare with a little extra making a big difference

ECONOMY SMART - our recommended fare with a little extra making a big difference
 Flight changes and refunds for a lower fee
 2 checked bags included
 Free of charge Standard seat selection
 Earn 75% FalconFlyer miles

* Cabin interior and features may not be exactly as shown

* Please refer to detailed fare rules for more information
* Please note that if the flight is operated by another airline then the onboard product or service may be different to that described above

ECONOMY LIGHT - the most affordable choice for customer who require less flexibility and services but who still wish to enjoy the full Gulf Air experience
 Highest charges for changes, cancellations or refunds
 2 checked bags included
 Additional fees for advance seat selection

Choose our SMART fare for more flexibility and free standard seat selection.

Benefit from more checked baggage allowance and more Q miles

Economy Classic includes                                                                                         
- 25kg checked baggage                                                                                     - Carry on 7kg (1 piece)                                                                                                   
- 50% Qmiles accumulation                                                                                                                                                 
- Refund to original form of payment (chargeable)                                                                                                                                       - Upgrade with Qmiles  
- 1 Date Change permitted, chargeable from 2nd Change                                                                                  
                                                                                                                        Please note that if the flight is operated by another airline then the on-board product or service maybe different to that described above.
Benefit from more Qmiles allowance and seat selection

Economy Convenience includes                                                                                           
- Checked baggage 2 x 23kg                                                                                     - Carry on 7kg (1 piece)                                                                                                   
- 75% Qmiles accumulation                                                                           
- Standard seat selection                                                                            
- Refund to original form of payment (chargeable)                                                                                                                                        - Upgrade with Qmiles    
-2 Date Change permitted, chargeable from 3rd Change                                                                                
                                                                                                                        Please note that if the flight is operated by another airline then the on-board product or service maybe different to that described above.
Upgrade to Economy Flex Plus to enjoy the full flexibility to make changes to your booking, enjoy more baggage allowance, choose your seats for free, and earn more Skywards Miles.

Economy Flex Plus includes:

 Free seat selection and paid seat selection
 Earn 1 Skywards Mile for every mile flown
 Checked baggage allowance
 Cabin baggage 1 bag up to 7kg
 Regional multicourse dining
 Complimentary alcoholic and non-alcoholic drinks
 Up to 5,000 channels of entertainment
 Free unlimited online chat messaging for Emirates Skywards Gold members 
 Buy great value Wi-Fi plans
 Eligible to upgrade with Skywards Miles 
 Changes permitted free of charge
 Fully refundable
